    "body" : "<p>Simple answer for your question is <strong>NO YOU CAN'T</strong> </p>\n\n<p><code>Once you are recording the only possible actions are stop and reset.</code></p>\n\n<p>So try to save your Call  to SDCard after you Stop , and then again start Fresh Record and Stop it. <code>Finally Combine both Audio File into one Audio file</code>.</p>\n\n<p>Record the audio as .wav file and <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/6179709/audio-appending-using-randomaccessfile\">Combine using this format</a>.</p>\n"
